{"tid":1212273,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"戰術討論-十八區游擊戰","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T20:23:25.000Z","uid":240303,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd91af285cd3a769725454cc6c0428e69416638f","tid":1212273,"uid":240303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"認同請幫推上熱門<br />\n<br />\n警狗 最大優勢係 裝備<br />\n我地 最大優勢係 人數<br />\n<br />\n人地堆重防我地先黎用土製裝備衝擊<br />\n裝備精良嘅警犬 係唔係有啲 以卵擊石<br />\n<br />\n將示威分散十八區  同日同時間開始<br />\n就算每個區只動員一兩千人都好<br />\n我就睇下係咪區區都出防暴  啲速龍識影分身都唔掂<br />\n再加上大家可以自組幾十人小隊  係唔同地方行動<br />\n就睇下佢守到幾多個點<br />\n<br />\n叫人分散預左比人話鬼  但一次佔中一次今日之後<br />\n我地係咪時候反思打法<br />\n（ps:共產黨最叻打游擊）"},{"pid":"655726397e0593a82e3dbd60ae7f83eb95ed2085","tid":1212273,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22b0b6310e07ac861e70e24e77a7a930795a2ba7","tid":1212273,"uid":240303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:56:50.000Z","msg":"再配合埋公共交通不合作運動，成效事半功倍"},{"pid":"ad315210d38c4e595db09b17b40db51fdc3fa0ef","tid":1212273,"uid":19613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fc9b498149061d3bd29f0e51beafb627210bab","tid":1212273,"uid":219297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:58:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212193</a><br />\n比個突破手段大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a8f2aed3c6220b5fdcd626d5ecdc5300510169","tid":1212273,"uid":110761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:00:55.000Z","msg":"噴黑D交通燈就走"},{"pid":"6063f6f26673feced24e2b144188f251e2faacad","tid":1212273,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"我決定呼籲各大市民鬧警行動<br />\n用口